    "Depending on what Blockchain is used, this could be many validator nodes.",
    "Decentralised finance (DeFi) is built upon automated protocols that offer financial services.",
    "DeFi solutions bring numerous advantages compared to traditional finance, including faster transaction speeds, improved transparency, interoperability, and immutability.",
    "However, these strengths also give rise to specific weaknesses.",
    "In other sections of this review, we explore the challenges of ensuring compliance with anti-money laundering processes when conducting cross-border transactions at high speeds."
